        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[哆啦A梦害怕]#陈乔恩13天没吃碳水# 碳水真的十恶不赦？还能不能让打工人好好干饭[抓狂]？作为一个碳水十级爱好者，阿卫必须要告诉大家，其实碳水也有好坏之分�...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[哆啦A梦害怕]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/doraemon/dr_03haipa-32e9b53caf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%99%88%E4%B9%94%E6%81%A913%E5%A4%A9%E6%B2%A1%E5%90%83%E7%A2%B3%E6%B0%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%99%88%E4%B9%94%E6%81%A913%E5%A4%A9%E6%B2%A1%E5%90%83%E7%A2%B3%E6%B0%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#陈乔恩13天没吃碳水#</span></a> 碳水真的十恶不赦？还能不能让打工人好好干饭<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>？作为一个碳水十级爱好者，阿卫必须要告诉大家，其实碳水也有好坏之分👇🏻<br><br>🙋🏻♂️好碳水：<br>富含纤维素、维生素和矿物质，在消化过程中分解较慢，血糖生成指数较低，对血糖的影响较小。容易出现饱腹感并减缓胃部排空的时间，还能为人体提供维生素和矿物质，对牙齿和肠道更健康。<br><br>🙅🏻♂️坏碳水：<br>富含高热量，纤维素、维生素和矿物质含量低，能在消化过程中迅速分解，转化为葡萄糖，使血糖达到峰值。摄入过多会增加心血管负担，增加患2型糖尿病的风险，不利于控制血压和体重。<br><br>碳水该咋吃？卫带着大家一起来看世卫组织发布的最新指南<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（健康中国）<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%8E%E7%A2%B3%E6%B0%B4%E9%A5%AE%E9%A3%9F%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%AA%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%8E%E7%A2%B3%E6%B0%B4%E9%A5%AE%E9%A3%9F%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%AA%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#低碳水饮食减肥有个前提#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnpdn2ytjuj20k00zkaeb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnpdn2zbenj20m81ybjzs.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hnpdn36wrxj20jg0h074z.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
